[{"Code":"en","Title":"Transfer sub-account balances","Slug":"transfer-balances","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"7f6d5e3f-6e76-444c-aa5e-eeb30e8386b9\"><img data-block-id=\"d245819f-d5cd-441c-94da-195e5e5f161b\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/accept-payment-for-eng(2).webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"654\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:654px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"0382eb85-34e8-46d0-94a8-1373f7b145a4\">With xenPlatform, you have full control over your merchant’s balance. You can transfer any amount of funds from your Mater Account to sub-accounts, and vice-versa.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"777\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:777px;width:777px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:203px;\"><col style=\"width:218px;\"><col style=\"width:356px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"fb96b746-74f4-4642-aedb-13582d2b35f8\">Source</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"939a3d89-dbc2-43e8-ac25-c8bbc5e3706e\">Destination</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><p data-block-id=\"ced12149-29e9-4de8-8a4e-07b5c3d88126\">Use Cases</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"ecb62a9d-1af8-428a-94ae-bfebf9969a25\">Master-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"a1a38189-122b-4f03-8095-dfacaecee2dc\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"7b05130a-128c-4748-95e7-d7e0a7e852aa\"><li data-block-id=\"64e882a6-cd64-49f3-b34b-3a7e7d493e2b\"><p data-block-id=\"76d1c4f9-1a1b-4b3d-8ce1-11cc704187b6\">Send bonuses</p></li><li data-block-id=\"afa64dea-960d-4427-a5a3-67268b650d6b\"><p data-block-id=\"047a970e-c29a-4ab9-a465-98b0c165ca41\">Send refunds</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5270825a-6a88-47cd-8dd3-65da82b2b187\"><p data-block-id=\"a32df5bc-9f14-4e3b-b1e4-fa8b130e33fe\">Top up merchant’s balance</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"5a38b3ea-fc2d-46bb-a247-f2752f093b6f\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"45e4baf9-a7ee-4bd7-93a8-1229e1868e4a\">Master-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"b9f64391-5bb9-49f9-af7a-f5cd1494fd55\"><li data-block-id=\"f03228fd-7968-4427-a409-850e12b7c0e4\"><p data-block-id=\"f3023ac7-8e34-4ec4-94ca-50bd4b6f3762\">Charge platform commission</p></li><li data-block-id=\"10130229-0531-49ad-ad88-de320d204c4f\"><p data-block-id=\"4d6e05b1-5845-45d0-bb7a-f2a7f48218d3\">Charge subscription fees</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8026eb6a-46f4-4d11-92cc-625da58c9aa8\"><p data-block-id=\"788a7604-e40b-4772-9b47-6fa50aa82a5c\">Charge management fees</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"a24dda75-563c-4992-87e1-a3d9e83e67ae\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"9ec9721a-f3be-4094-9c01-f2d51b7ca9c4\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"3a2b4db9-c663-44f6-a8f0-05ea7ae70e33\"><li data-block-id=\"7e77fe58-168e-4939-87f2-0bcd47b6c94b\"><p data-block-id=\"d1675a96-ad36-4ea2-b69b-5f998a82ce20\">Facilitate reselling or drop shipping</p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"micp84n3-wyufdh-005\">Region Support for Global Accounts</h2><p data-block-id=\"micp84n3-p7s0o5-006\">Cross-border transfers and split payments (between accounts incorporated in different countries) are not supported for merchants incorporated in <emoji data-name=\"flag-id\" title=\"Indonesia Flag\" data-unicode-version=\"1F1EE-1F1E9\">🇮🇩</emoji> Indonesia. You may still transfer funds between accounts incorporated in the same country.</p><p data-block-id=\"micp84n3-ctiy87-007\">Additionally, transfers and split payments can only be made between balances of the same currency. You may use the conversion feature before or afterwards to convert currencies.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"c9455c50-c87b-470e-9cd8-8737e10f149d\">How to create transfers</h2><p data-block-id=\"55df889e-efc4-4444-bec9-1d823d6d352b\"><strong>Via dashboard:</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"06bf020b-e73c-4908-86c7-d09b8b6b953d\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"0c92125b-76bd-4c18-a026-b6dcf01400f7\"><p data-block-id=\"a1216d0e-aa4b-4786-932f-c478454d5189\">Navigate to the xenPlatform Accounts page</p></li><li data-block-id=\"148ecaba-01ef-4b5d-9303-613d4242c83a\"><p data-block-id=\"777ce53d-2af3-4cc9-a2a9-8ef624026cdb\">Click the <strong>Create transfer</strong> button</p></li><li data-block-id=\"6517a7a7-9829-443b-9d86-28375de99fb7\"><p data-block-id=\"21a03f56-98b9-44a7-9213-c564da2e8854\">Fill in the required fields</p><ol data-block-id=\"813ef1fd-ef79-4ab3-8cb6-82532f038f31\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"68d8184f-f91f-4139-aa0c-491ac93663fd\"><p data-block-id=\"4a7e3d12-6bb9-4c00-a458-e8af84dcd8ab\"><code>From</code>: account ID or name where the funds are transferred from</p></li><li data-block-id=\"1681e640-fa0a-4661-9ece-70ccf8c4aa21\"><p data-block-id=\"97033864-0bf5-48d5-b5d3-a354f4e7c0a2\"><code>To</code>: account ID or name where the funds are transferred to</p></li><li data-block-id=\"43055bd9-f561-46db-a1dc-d64dc387b27e\"><p data-block-id=\"f2cf5dd0-3b71-4418-8a41-6ca59d46e227\"><code>Amounts to transfer</code>: the amount of funds of your choice</p></li><li data-block-id=\"f3c8406f-4278-4203-82e1-bb0582e539e9\"><p data-block-id=\"13d13f33-2aad-4ee1-9503-a0ef4a1bc3f7\"><code>Reference</code>: a unique identifier of the transfer</p></li></ol></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"b523f6bc-b482-416f-8d04-70155f456924\"><strong>Via API:</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"9e6b4667-df6c-45a1-93da-9e048bba10dc\">To create transfer via API, you will need to specify the required parameters:</p><ul data-block-id=\"3eea4db7-bd61-48f5-85fb-054f66499372\"><li data-block-id=\"4876a98f-e765-43cf-8233-774a7fad9822\"><p data-block-id=\"cc7cc753-a22d-4692-be4c-bc65a8fc9323\"><code>reference</code>: a unique identifier of this transfer for reconciliation purposes</p></li><li data-block-id=\"2b3bf302-1cc6-4e6f-aef0-0d87a72ba2dc\"><p data-block-id=\"7d809edf-1dca-4b9c-9363-ed011696c8e9\"><code>amount</code>: the amount you would like to transfer</p></li><li data-block-id=\"a22247a9-681b-46a8-b94a-8ca98f782434\"><p data-block-id=\"8c4052b3-10ba-45d0-aec3-5cd4f8dafb80\"><code>source_user_id</code>: the account balance from which you would like to send the Transfer from</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5a2dd7b6-664e-4fb5-8dcf-4388c6da706d\"><p data-block-id=\"0a0e322b-6eab-457b-9578-f8af0eb03482\"><code>destination_user_id</code>: the account balance from which you would like to send the Transfer to</p></li></ul><pre data-block-id=\"e6a2598b-b181-4314-841b-7f6158862250\" language=\"bash\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\" spellcheck=\"false\">curl --request POST \\\n  --url POST https://api.xendit.co/transfers \\\n  --data '{\n\"reference\":\"2020-nov-subscription-fee\",\n\"amount\":10000,\n\"source_user_id\":\"5cafeb170a2b18519b1b8768\",\n\"destination_user_id\":\"5f8d0c0603ffe06b7d4d9fcf\"\n}'</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"ed9cfdb4-5cdf-4bc5-9a46-5042c1509b33\">Notes on transfers:</p><ul data-block-id=\"4ef46337-9911-4df9-ae69-6083bc166bbc\"><li data-block-id=\"420f2f6f-c75e-46e4-8710-9abdc28b46a0\"><p data-block-id=\"4876108b-bb5a-4a83-b853-51670cbcf630\">All transfers will be executed immediately</p></li><li data-block-id=\"4adc8d66-87b8-4c2c-8f15-2bca6867521f\"><p data-block-id=\"f5955858-1ae2-44de-b917-5d0f7d62fc67\">Transfer amount should be less than the total balance of the sender’s account</p></li><li data-block-id=\"53629c7a-f0df-4c46-9740-8eadb57b9257\"><p data-block-id=\"8f0847e3-e0bd-4600-a158-739d528c01fb\">Transfer amount needs to be an absolute number</p></li><li data-block-id=\"949cb752-421b-4c62-b35e-109847b9a1fd\"><p data-block-id=\"c0aded30-bd6b-4eee-b573-3234847e0c1a\">You can only create transfers using the Master-Account's API key. Sub-Accounts that you manage through xenPlatform have no ability to create transfers through this endpoint.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"micp80di-8e3z3b-004\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Transfer sub-account balances","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Transfer saldo sub-akun","Slug":"transfer-balances","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8j8-7tn2to-925\"><img data-block-id=\"mcs0t8j8-nr5rvk-926\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/accept-payment-for-eng(2).webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"654\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:654px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8j9-j4m0kx-927\">Dengan xenPlatform, Anda memiliki kendali penuh atas saldo merchant Anda. Anda dapat mentransfer dana dalam jumlah berapa pun dari Akun Masterke sub-akun, dan sebaliknya.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"777\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:777px;width:777px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:203px;\"><col style=\"width:218px;\"><col style=\"width:356px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ja-wxz14n-928\">Sumber</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ja-5wklzd-929\">Tujuan</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ja-0mzv64-930\">Kasus Penggunaan</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ja-sstbpu-931\">Akun Master</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ja-bbt9tx-932\">Sub-Akun</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jb-jg2645-933\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jb-zkathb-934\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jb-au5d4z-935\">Mengirim bonus</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jb-bqzi9n-936\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jb-125lzr-937\">Mengirim pengembalian dana</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jb-i88u7w-938\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jb-gjftre-939\">Top up saldo merchant</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-itypad-940\">Sub-Akun</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-0h3yll-941\">Akun Master</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-zoqpn1-942\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-6qk8iu-943\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-yt3hx0-944\">Biaya komisi platform</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-cq813l-945\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-g8h5x4-946\">Membebankan biaya berlangganan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-si1ndl-947\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jc-967lo8-948\">Membebankan biaya manajemen</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jh-sbbx1c-949\">Sub-Akun</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jh-7uts5z-950\">Sub-Akun</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jh-25g0lb-951\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jh-lesz16-952\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jh-majyq2-953\">Memfasilitasi penjualan kembali atau pengiriman drop</p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ji-jf1jiq-954\">Cara membuat transfer</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ji-l7fzul-955\"><strong>Melalui dasbor:</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ji-enimdm-956\" start=\"1\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ji-uea2rq-957\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ji-srgb8y-958\">Buka Akun xenPlatform</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ji-5qczag-959\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8ji-l180xy-960\">Klik tombol <strong>Buat transfer</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jj-t7xyce-961\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jj-bhlpl1-962\">Isi kolom yang wajib diisi</p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jj-dqqkkl-963\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jj-61zi22-964\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jj-bhmhtt-965\"><code>From</code>: ID akun atau nama tempat dana ditransfer</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jj-3cis1z-966\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jj-txk4m2-967\"><code>To</code>: ID akun atau nama tempat dana ditransfer</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-0iqxr6-968\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-hc3s7f-969\"><code>Amounts to transfer</code>: jumlah dana pilihan Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-u7qkww-970\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-t9wb7k-971\"><code>Reference</code>: pengidentifikasi unik transfer</p></li></ol></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-u02bbq-972\"><strong>Melalui API:</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-dpaoqs-973\">Untuk membuat transfer melalui API, Anda harus menentukan parameter yang diperlukan:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-i58s3u-974\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-o4ma56-975\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-i4lg91-976\"><code>reference</code>: pengidentifikasi unik transfer ini untuk tujuan rekonsiliasi</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-nij7b7-977\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-td1h3l-978\"><code>amount</code>: jumlah yang ingin Anda transfer</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-wdom86-979\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jk-dgtxrv-980\"><code>source_user_id</code>: saldo akun dari mana Anda ingin mengirim Transfer</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jl-ksfku6-981\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jl-6lkog2-982\"><code>destination_user_id</code>: saldo akun tempat Anda ingin mengirim Transfer</p></li></ul><pre data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jl-w5weel-983\" language=\"bash\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\" spellcheck=\"false\">curl --request POST \\\n  --url POST https://api.xendit.co/transfers \\\n  --data '{\n\"reference\":\"2020-nov-subscription-fee\",\n\"amount\":10000,\n\"source_user_id\":\"5cafeb170a2b18519b1b8768\",\n\"destination_user_id\":\"5f8d0c0603ffe06b7d4d9fcf\"\n}'</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-2gifr2-984\">Catatan tentang transfer:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-vbbwa9-985\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-86yr4m-986\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-x24awd-987\">Semua transfer akan segera dieksekusi</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-t6ryz3-988\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-5pcfro-989\">Jumlah transfer harus kurang dari total saldo akun pengirim</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-58jfjn-990\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-i1g689-991\">Jumlah transfer harus berupa angka absolut</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-jhfty9-992\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-t3t9yz-993\">Anda hanya dapat membuat transfer menggunakan API key Akun Master. Sub-Akun yang Anda kelola melalui xenPlatform tidak memiliki kemampuan untuk membuat transfer melalui endpoint ini.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mcs0t8jm-rbk275-994\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Transfer saldo sub-akun","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"การโอนยอดคงเหลือของบัญชีรอง (Sub-account balances)","Slug":"transfer-between-accounts","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"7f6d5e3f-6e76-444c-aa5e-eeb30e8386b9\"><img data-block-id=\"d245819f-d5cd-441c-94da-195e5e5f161b\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/accept-payment-for-eng(2).webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"654\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:654px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"0382eb85-34e8-46d0-94a8-1373f7b145a4\">ด้วย xenPlatform คุณสามารถควบคุมยอดคงเหลือ (balance) ของร้านค้า (merchant) ของคุณได้อย่างสมบูรณ์ คุณสามารถโอนเงินจำนวนเท่าใดก็ได้จาก Master Account ของคุณไปยัง sub-accounts และในทางกลับกัน</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"777\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:777px;width:777px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:203px;\"><col style=\"width:218px;\"><col style=\"width:356px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"fb96b746-74f4-4642-aedb-13582d2b35f8\">ต้นทาง</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"939a3d89-dbc2-43e8-ac25-c8bbc5e3706e\">ปลายทาง</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><p data-block-id=\"ced12149-29e9-4de8-8a4e-07b5c3d88126\">กรณีการใช้งาน</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"ecb62a9d-1af8-428a-94ae-bfebf9969a25\">Master-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"a1a38189-122b-4f03-8095-dfacaecee2dc\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"7b05130a-128c-4748-95e7-d7e0a7e852aa\" style><li data-block-id=\"64e882a6-cd64-49f3-b34b-3a7e7d493e2b\"><p data-block-id=\"76d1c4f9-1a1b-4b3d-8ce1-11cc704187b6\">ส่งโบนัส</p></li><li data-block-id=\"afa64dea-960d-4427-a5a3-67268b650d6b\"><p data-block-id=\"047a970e-c29a-4ab9-a465-98b0c165ca41\">ส่งเงินคืน (refunds)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5270825a-6a88-47cd-8dd3-65da82b2b187\"><p data-block-id=\"a32df5bc-9f14-4e3b-b1e4-fa8b130e33fe\">เติมเงินเข้ายอดคงเหลือ (balance) ของร้านค้า (merchant)</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"5a38b3ea-fc2d-46bb-a247-f2752f093b6f\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"45e4baf9-a7ee-4bd7-93a8-1229e1868e4a\">Master-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"b9f64391-5bb9-49f9-af7a-f5cd1494fd55\" style><li data-block-id=\"f03228fd-7968-4427-a409-850e12b7c0e4\"><p data-block-id=\"f3023ac7-8e34-4ec4-94ca-50bd4b6f3762\">เรียกเก็บค่าคอมมิชชัน (commission) ของแพลตฟอร์ม</p></li><li data-block-id=\"10130229-0531-49ad-ad88-de320d204c4f\"><p data-block-id=\"4d6e05b1-5845-45d0-bb7a-f2a7f48218d3\">เรียกเก็บค่าธรรมเนียมการสมัครสมาชิก (subscription fees)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8026eb6a-46f4-4d11-92cc-625da58c9aa8\"><p data-block-id=\"788a7604-e40b-4772-9b47-6fa50aa82a5c\">เรียกเก็บค่าธรรมเนียมการจัดการ (management fees)</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"a24dda75-563c-4992-87e1-a3d9e83e67ae\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"9ec9721a-f3be-4094-9c01-f2d51b7ca9c4\">Sub-Account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"3a2b4db9-c663-44f6-a8f0-05ea7ae70e33\" style><li data-block-id=\"7e77fe58-168e-4939-87f2-0bcd47b6c94b\"><p data-block-id=\"d1675a96-ad36-4ea2-b69b-5f998a82ce20\">อำนวยความสะดวกในการขายต่อ (reselling) หรือการดรอปชิป (drop shipping)</p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"c9455c50-c87b-470e-9cd8-87370f149d\">วิธีสร้างการโอนเงิน (transfers)</h2><p data-block-id=\"55df889e-efc4-4444-bec9-1d823d6d352b\"><strong>ผ่านแดชบอร์ด (dashboard):</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"06bf020b-e73c-4908-86c7-d09b8b6b953d\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"0c92125b-76bd-4c18-a026-b6dcf01400f7\"><p data-block-id=\"a1216d0e-aa4b-4786-932f-c478454d5189\">ไปที่หน้า xenPlatform Accounts</p></li><li data-block-id=\"148ecaba-01ef-4b5d-9303-613d4242c83a\"><p data-block-id=\"777ce53d-2af3-4cc9-a2a9-8ef624026cdb\">คลิกปุ่ม <strong>Create transfer</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"6517a7a7-9829-443b-9d86-28375de99fb7\"><p data-block-id=\"21a03f56-98b9-44a7-9213-c564da2e8854\">กรอกข้อมูลในช่องที่จำเป็น</p><ol data-block-id=\"813ef1fd-ef79-4ab3-8cb6-82532f038f31\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"68d8184f-f91f-4139-aa0c-491ac93663fd\"><p data-block-id=\"4a7e3d12-6bb9-4c00-a458-e8af84dcd8ab\"><code>From</code>: ID หรือชื่อบัญชีที่เป็นต้นทางของการโอนเงิน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"1681e640-fa0a-4661-9ece-70ccf8c4aa21\"><p data-block-id=\"97033864-0bf5-48d5-b5d3-a354f4e7c0a2\"><code>To</code>: ID หรือชื่อบัญชีที่เป็นปลายทางของการโอนเงิน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"43055bd9-f561-46db-a1dc-d64dc387b27e\"><p data-block-id=\"f2cf5dd0-3b71-4418-8a41-6ca59d46e227\"><code>Amounts to transfer</code>: จำนวนเงินที่คุณต้องการโอน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"f3c8406f-4278-4203-82e1-bb0582e539e9\"><p data-block-id=\"13d13f33-2aad-4ee1-9503-a0ef4a1bc3f7\"><code>Reference</code>: ตัวระบุเฉพาะ (unique identifier) ของการโอนเงิน</p></li></ol></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"b523f6bc-b482-416f-8d04-70155f456924\"><strong>ผ่าน API:</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"9e6b4667-df6c-45a1-93da-9e048bba10dc\">ในการสร้างการโอนเงินผ่าน API คุณจะต้องระบุพารามิเตอร์ (parameters) ที่จำเป็นดังนี้:</p><ul data-block-id=\"3eea4db7-bd61-48f5-85fb-054f66499372\" style><li data-block-id=\"4876a98f-e765-43cf-8233-774a7fad9822\"><p data-block-id=\"cc7cc753-a22d-4692-be4c-bc65a8fc9323\"><code>reference</code>: ตัวระบุเฉพาะ (unique identifier) ของการโอนเงินนี้เพื่อวัตถุประสงค์ในการกระทบยอด (reconciliation)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"2b3bf302-1cc6-4e6f-aef0-0d87a72ba2dc\"><p data-block-id=\"7d809edf-1dca-4b9c-9363-ed011696c8e9\"><code>amount</code>: จำนวนเงินที่คุณต้องการโอน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"a22247a9-681b-46a8-b94a-8ca98f782434\"><p data-block-id=\"8c4052b3-10ba-45d0-aec3-5cd4f8dafb80\"><code>source_user_id</code>: ยอดคงเหลือ (balance) ของบัญชีที่คุณต้องการส่งการโอนเงินจาก</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5a2dd7b6-664e-4fb5-8dcf-4388c6da706d\"><p data-block-id=\"0a0e322b-6eab-457b-9578-f8af0eb03482\"><code>destination_user_id</code>: ยอดคงเหลือ (balance) ของบัญชีที่คุณต้องการส่งการโอนเงินไป</p></li></ul><pre data-block-id=\"e6a2598b-b181-4314-841b-7f6158862250\" language=\"bash\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\" spellcheck=\"false\">curl --request POST \\\n  --url POST https://api.xendit.co/transfers \\\n  --data &apos;{\n&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;2020-nov-subscription-fee&quot;,\n&quot;amount&quot;:10000,\n&quot;source_user_id&quot;:&quot;5cafeb170a2b18519b1b8768&quot;,\n&quot;destination_user_id&quot;:&quot;5f8d0c0603ffe06b7d4d9fcf&quot;\n}&apos;</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"ed9cfdb4-5cdf-4bc5-9a46-5042c1509b33\">ข้อควรทราบเกี่ยวกับการโอนเงิน (transfers):</p><ul data-block-id=\"4ef46337-9911-4df9-ae69-6083bc166bbc\" style><li data-block-id=\"420f2f6f-c75e-46e4-8710-9abdc28b46a0\"><p data-block-id=\"4876108b-bb5a-4a83-b853-51670cbcf630\">การโอนเงินทั้งหมดจะดำเนินการทันที</p></li><li data-block-id=\"4adc8d66-87b8-4c2c-8f15-2bca6867521f\"><p data-block-id=\"f5955858-1ae2-44de-b917-5d0f7d62fc67\">จำนวนเงินที่โอนควรน้อยกว่ายอดคงเหลือ (balance) ทั้งหมดของบัญชีผู้ส่ง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"53629c7a-f0df-4c46-9740-8eadb57b9257\"><p data-block-id=\"8f0847e3-e0bd-4600-a158-739d528c01fb\">จำนวนเงินที่โอนต้องเป็นจำนวนเต็มบวก (absolute number)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"949cb752-421b-4c62-b35e-109847b9a1fd\"><p data-block-id=\"c0aded30-bd6b-4eee-b573-3234847e0c1a\">คุณสามารถสร้างการโอนเงินได้โดยใช้ API key ของ Master-Account เท่านั้น Sub-Accounts ที่คุณจัดการผ่าน xenPlatform ไม่สามารถสร้างการโอนเงินผ่าน endpoint นี้ได้</p></li></ul><p></p>","SeoTitle":"การโอนยอดคงเหลือของบัญชีรอง (Sub-account balances)","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Transferencia de saldos de subcuentas","Slug":"transfer-balances","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"7f6d5e3f-6e76-444c-aa5e-eeb30e8386b9\"><img data-block-id=\"d245819f-d5cd-441c-94da-195e5e5f161b\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/accept-payment-for-eng(2).webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"654\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:654px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"0382eb85-34e8-46d0-94a8-1373f7b145a4\">Con xenPlatform, usted tiene control total sobre el saldo de su Comercio. Puede transferir cualquier Monto de fondos desde su Cuenta Maestra a Subcuentas, y viceversa.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"777\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:777px;width:777px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:203px;\"><col style=\"width:218px;\"><col style=\"width:356px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"fb96b746-74f4-4642-aedb-13582d2b35f8\">Origen</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"939a3d89-dbc2-43e8-ac25-c8bbc5e3706e\">Destino</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><p data-block-id=\"ced12149-29e9-4de8-8a4e-07b5c3d88126\">Casos de Uso</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"ecb62a9d-1af8-428a-94ae-bfebf9969a25\">Cuenta Maestra</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"a1a38189-122b-4f03-8095-dfacaecee2dc\">Subcuenta</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"7b05130a-128c-4748-95e7-d7e0a7e852aa\" style><li data-block-id=\"64e882a6-cd64-49f3-b34b-3a7e7d493e2b\"><p data-block-id=\"76d1c4f9-1a1b-4b3d-8ce1-11cc704187b6\">Enviar bonificaciones</p></li><li data-block-id=\"afa64dea-960d-4427-a5a3-67268b650d6b\"><p data-block-id=\"047a970e-c29a-4ab9-a465-98b0c165ca41\">Enviar reembolsos</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5270825a-6a88-47cd-8dd3-65da82b2b187\"><p data-block-id=\"a32df5bc-9f14-4e3b-b1e4-fa8b130e33fe\">Recargar el saldo del Comercio</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"5a38b3ea-fc2d-46bb-a247-f2752f093b6f\">Subcuenta</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"45e4baf9-a7ee-4bd7-93a8-1229e1868e4a\">Cuenta Maestra</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"b9f64391-5bb9-49f9-af7a-f5cd1494fd55\" style><li data-block-id=\"f03228fd-7968-4427-a409-850e12b7c0e4\"><p data-block-id=\"f3023ac7-8e34-4ec4-94ca-50bd4b6f3762\">Cobrar comisión de la plataforma</p></li><li data-block-id=\"10130229-0531-49ad-ad88-de320d204c4f\"><p data-block-id=\"4d6e05b1-5845-45d0-bb7a-f2a7f48218d3\">Cobrar tarifas de suscripción</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8026eb6a-46f4-4d11-92cc-625da58c9aa8\"><p data-block-id=\"788a7604-e40b-4772-9b47-6fa50aa82a5c\">Cobrar tarifas de gestión</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"203\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"a24dda75-563c-4992-87e1-a3d9e83e67ae\">Subcuenta</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"218\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><p data-block-id=\"9ec9721a-f3be-4094-9c01-f2d51b7ca9c4\">Subcuenta</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"356\"><ul data-block-id=\"3a2b4db9-c663-44f6-a8f0-05ea7ae70e33\" style><li data-block-id=\"7e77fe58-168e-4939-87f2-0bcd47b6c94b\"><p data-block-id=\"d1675a96-ad36-4ea2-b69b-5f998a82ce20\">Facilitar la reventa o el drop shipping</p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"c9455c50-c87b-470e-9cd8-8737e10f149d\">Cómo crear transferencias</h2><p data-block-id=\"55df889e-efc4-4444-bec9-1d823d6d352b\"><strong>A través del dashboard:</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"06bf020b-e73c-4908-86c7-d09b8b6b953d\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"0c92125b-76bd-4c18-a026-b6dcf01400f7\"><p data-block-id=\"a1216d0e-aa4b-4786-932f-c478454d5189\">Navegue a la página de Cuentas de xenPlatform</p></li><li data-block-id=\"148ecaba-01ef-4b5d-9303-613d4242c83a\"><p data-block-id=\"777ce53d-2af3-4cc9-a2a9-8ef624026cdb\">Haga clic en el botón <strong>Crear transferencia</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"6517a7a7-9829-443b-9d86-28375de99fb7\"><p data-block-id=\"21a03f56-98b9-44a7-9213-c564da2e8854\">Complete los campos obligatorios</p><ol data-block-id=\"813ef1fd-ef79-4ab3-8cb6-82532f038f31\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"68d8184f-f91f-4139-aa0c-491ac93663fd\"><p data-block-id=\"4a7e3d12-6bb9-4c00-a458-e8af84dcd8ab\"><code>From</code>: ID o Nombre de la Cuenta desde donde se transfieren los fondos</p></li><li data-block-id=\"1681e640-fa0a-4661-9ece-70ccf8c4aa21\"><p data-block-id=\"97033864-0bf5-48d5-b5d3-a354f4e7c0a2\"><code>To</code>: ID o Nombre de la Cuenta a donde se transfieren los fondos</p></li><li data-block-id=\"43055bd9-f561-46db-a1dc-d64dc387b27e\"><p data-block-id=\"f2cf5dd0-3b71-4418-8a41-6ca59d46e227\"><code>Amounts to transfer</code>: el Monto de fondos de su elección</p></li><li data-block-id=\"f3c8406f-4278-4203-82e1-bb0582e539e9\"><p data-block-id=\"13d13f33-2aad-4ee1-9503-a0ef4a1bc3f7\"><code>Reference</code>: un identificador único de la Transferencia</p></li></ol></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"b523f6bc-b482-416f-8d04-70155f456924\"><strong>A través de la API:</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"9e6b4667-df6c-45a1-93da-9e048bba10dc\">Para Crear una Transferencia a través de la API, usted deberá especificar los parámetros obligatorios:</p><ul data-block-id=\"3eea4db7-bd61-48f5-85fb-054f66499372\" style><li data-block-id=\"4876a98f-e765-43cf-8233-774a7fad9822\"><p data-block-id=\"cc7cc753-a22d-4692-be4c-bc65a8fc9323\"><code>reference</code>: un identificador único de esta Transferencia para fines de conciliación</p></li><li data-block-id=\"2b3bf302-1cc6-4e6f-aef0-0d87a72ba2dc\"><p data-block-id=\"7d809edf-1dca-4b9c-9363-ed011696c8e9\"><code>amount</code>: el Monto que desea transferir</p></li><li data-block-id=\"a22247a9-681b-46a8-b94a-8ca98f782434\"><p data-block-id=\"8c4052b3-10ba-45d0-aec3-5cd4f8dafb80\"><code>source_user_id</code>: el Saldo de la Cuenta desde la que desea Enviar la Transferencia</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5a2dd7b6-664e-4fb5-8dcf-4388c6da706d\"><p data-block-id=\"0a0e322b-6eab-457b-9578-f8af0eb03482\"><code>destination_user_id</code>: el Saldo de la Cuenta a la que desea Enviar la Transferencia</p></li></ul><pre data-block-id=\"e6a2598b-b181-4314-841b-7f6158862250\" language=\"bash\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\" spellcheck=\"false\">curl --request POST \\\n  --url POST https://api.xendit.co/transfers \\\n  --data &apos;{\n&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;2020-nov-subscription-fee&quot;,\n&quot;amount&quot;:10000,\n&quot;source_user_id&quot;:&quot;5cafeb170a2b18519b1b8768&quot;,\n&quot;destination_user_id&quot;:&quot;5f8d0c0603ffe06b7d4d9fcf&quot;\n}&apos;</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"ed9cfdb4-5cdf-4bc5-9a46-5042c1509b33\">Notas sobre las transferencias:</p><ul data-block-id=\"4ef46337-9911-4df9-ae69-6083bc166bbc\" style><li data-block-id=\"420f2f6f-c75e-46e4-8710-9abdc2b46a0\"><p data-block-id=\"4876108b-bb5a-4a83-b853-51670cbcf630\">Todas las transferencias se ejecutarán inmediatamente</p></li><li data-block-id=\"4adc8d66-87b8-4c2c-8f15-2bca6867521f\"><p data-block-id=\"f5955858-1ae2-44de-b917-5d0f7d62fc67\">El Monto de la Transferencia debe ser menor que el Saldo total de la Cuenta del remitente</p></li><li data-block-id=\"53629c7a-f0df-4c46-9740-8eadb57b9257\"><p data-block-id=\"8f0847e3-e0bd-4600-a158-739d528c01fb\">El Monto de la Transferencia debe ser un número absoluto</p></li><li data-block-id=\"949cb752-421b-4c62-b35e-109847b9a1fd\"><p data-block-id=\"c0aded30-bd6b-4eee-b573-3234847e0c1a\">Solo puede Crear transferencias utilizando la API key de la Cuenta Maestra. Las Subcuentas que usted gestiona a través de xenPlatform no tienen la capacidad de Crear transferencias a través de este endpoint.</p></li></ul><p></p>","SeoTitle":"Transferencia de saldos de subcuentas","Description":null}]